headline: Kinder Morgan Surges 52.7% in a Year: Should You Still Buy the Stock?
summary: As a leading midstream service provider, Kinder Morgan's pipeline and storage assets are secured under long-term take-or-pay contracts, generating almost two-thirds of its EBITDA.
